\end_inset

 data je sa:
 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
r_{i_{Q}}(v,\varphi)=-v^{2}_{i}y_{ii}\sin(\theta_{ii})+v_{i}\sum^{n}_{j=1,\,j\ne i}y_{ij}v_{j}\sin(\varphi_{i}-\theta_{ij}-\varphi_{j})-\hat{q}_{i}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\noindent
gdje su 
